{"tid":303521,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[CARAT] SAY THE NAME!! SEVENTEEN 17 討論區(8) 812香港場","createTime":"2017-06-30T08:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T16:37:12.000Z","uid":116634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d3c41af654e8e1525d4fd181f36f5ad0de9bedc0","tid":303521,"uid":116634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:53:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.hizliresim.com/j8dOgr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.hizliresim.com%2Fj8dOgr.jpg&h=ac9fc148&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.allkpop.com/upload/2017/05/af_org/28200254/Seventeen.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.allkpop.com%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2Faf_org%2F28200254%2FSeventeen.jpg&h=3444a329&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.funcurve.com/wp-content/uploads/Seventeen_Going_Seventeen_cover.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.funcurve.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FSeventeen_Going_Seventeen_cover.jpg&h=b31f5e60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.allkpop.com/upload/2016/07/af_org/Seventeen_1468712437_af_org.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.allkpop.com%2Fupload%2F2016%2F07%2Faf_org%2FSeventeen_1468712437_af_org.jpg&h=bacecff0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://0.soompi.io/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/10161103/seventeen.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F0.soompi.io%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F04%2F10161103%2Fseventeen.jpg&h=6843de2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/9M7k9ZV67c0/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F9M7k9ZV67c0%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=b569c953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/gSROYxg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgSROYxg.jpg&h=8fd0722b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">召集連登既CARAT入嚟等睇香港場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">SEVENTEEN（세븐틴）是韓國Pledis Entertainment公司旗下的13人男子流行音樂團體，成員包括S.COUPS、淨漢、Joshua、Jun、Hoshi、圓佑、Woozi、DK、珉奎、The8、勝寛、Vernon、Dino。2015年5月26日透過Debut Showcase正式出道，並於5月29日發行首張迷你專輯《17 Carat》，主打曲為《Adore U》。由於成員不論是編曲、編舞和作詞，均實際參與到每一張專輯的製作，出色的創作實力使SEVENTEEN獲得「自給自足偶像(자체제작 아이돌)」的稱號。<br />\n團體名字「SEVENTEEN」的寓意為「13名成員+3個分隊+1個團體=17」。歌迷被稱為「캐럿 (CARAT) 」，名稱取於鑽石的質量單位。寓意是SEVENTEEN像鑽石一樣閃耀的存在，隨著CARAT的數字增加，SEVENTEEN的價值也就越高。</span></div>"},{"pid":"2e46dab39331ebdb044c8c18d5ea47024e088587","tid":303521,"uid":116634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:55:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\">成員介紹</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">HIP-HOP TEAM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nS.COUPS<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.seventeen-17.com/upload/board/file/FILE20161213140830(1).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.seventeen-17.com%2Fupload%2Fboard%2Ffile%2FFILE20161213140830%281%29.jpg&h=3633f4ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/originals/54/51/34/5451349863236c4bee6bcfe91fee9acb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F54%2F51%2F34%2F5451349863236c4bee6bcfe91fee9acb.jpg&h=b8794e92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姓名：崔勝澈 최승철 / Choi Seung Cheol<br />\n生日：1995年8月8日（21歲）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWONWOO 圓佑<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.seventeen-17.com/upload/board/file/FILE20161213141126(1).jpg\" data-thumbnail-s